Inspired by: [Zander Martineau's Placeholders] (https://github.com/mrmartineau/)

***Lazy Installation***

1. Download package
2. [on Mac] Copy to Users/yourusername/Library/Application Support/Sublime Text 2/Packages

or

1. Open Terminal
2. cd ~/Library/Application\ Support/Sublime\ Text\ 2/Packages
3. git clone https://github.com/CristinaSolana/sublipsum.git

***How invoke a 'Tab Trigger'***

1. type tabs trigger, for example, img
2. Press [TAB] button
3. Choose desired placeholder

**Tab Triggers**

Trigger: **form**  
`<form>` + form elements: inputs (text, email, url, tel, radio, checkbox), select list, text area, button

Trigger: **img**  
`<img>` with placehold.it image

Trigger: **table**  
`<table>` (sample data coming)

Trigger: **nav**  
`<nav>` with nested `<ul>`

**Lists**

Trigger: **dl**  
`<dl>`

Trigger: **ol**  
`<ol>`

Trigger: **ul**  
`<ul>`

Trigger: **page**  
Page content including: `<h1>` `<h2>` `<h3>` `<p>` `<blockquote>` `<ul>`

**Paragraphs**

Trigger: **p**  
`<p>` Short (one sentence)

Trigger: **p**  
`<p>` Medium (5 sentences)

Trigger: **p**  
`<p>` Long (10 sentences)